{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"48640-rose-and-rocky-go-green","title":"Rose and Rocky Go Green","description":"Rose has a recipe to turn waste into plant food. Join Rose and Rocky in their adventures in this book about composting.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Annie Besant"],"illustrators":["Sandhya Prabhat"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/48640-rose-and-rocky-go-green"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/714300/size3/cb3c6c8b6d1b8b96716c58435660e6cb.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/714300/size6/cb3c6c8b6d1b8b96716c58435660e6cb.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86642/size6/eda04052cf5f6ca7c4b19334c31f0274.jpg","text":"Rose came home from school with a new idea.\n“Appa! I know how to make compost!”","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86643/size6/d6352c9ae0819d042155fe88396552a4.jpg","text":"“What is compost?” asked Appa, scratching his head.\n“Can I make it in the backyard, Appa?” Rose asked, tugging Rocky’s ear.\n“But what is compost?” Appa asked, scratching his ear.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86647/size6/a6d012c50ffa8974f2899400b343a0ef.jpg","text":"“It’s what plants eat, Appa,” said Rose. It makes them grow tall and strong.”\n“Baaaaa! Even I knew that!” bleated Rocky.\nAppa looked worried.\n“Oh, don't worry, Appa. All I need to make compost is waste.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86630/size6/73855318fc171cfd3f6df132df4f2f19.jpg","text":"Off they ran to the backyard to dig a hole.\n“Do you know what we need for compost, Rocky?”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86631/size6/0deabc2000e43714f73801140bae698e.jpg","text":"“We need lots of vegetable and fruit peels. See, we don't have to waste anything any more!\"","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86857/size6/c628fd9ac4ddcb42dfc8a4898d567315.jpg","text":"“We need lots \nof newspapers!”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86858/size6/9143c9cca089ecb721236a7356535cd5.jpg","text":"“We need dry leaves!”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86636/size6/c3ed8afd8976e6319c24aef72efb2a4b.jpg","text":"“And we \nneed water!”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86646/size6/2e3d56303689a044840baf9dd1f3180a.jpg","text":"10/12","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86639/size6/35dbec653456f8c62a92bbb7033c8c0f.jpg","text":"“Where did everything go?”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86640/size6/e6f3c51b40ab743170be7128260c0af8.jpg","text":"“ROCKY!”","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":137}}